{
  "bookId": "laozi-wangbi-wiki",
  "num": 2,
  "title": "第二章",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "天下皆知美之為美，斯惡已。皆知善之為善，斯不善已。故有無相生，難易相成，長短相較，高下相傾，音聲相和，前後相隨。"
    },
    {
      "text": "是以聖人處無為之事，"
    },
    {
      "text": "行不言之教；萬物作焉而不辭，生而不有，為而不恃，"
    },
    {
      "text": "功成而弗居。"
    },
    {
      "text": "夫唯弗居，是以不去。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "wangbi": [
      {
        "id": "wangbi-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 56
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "美者，人心之所進樂也；惡者，人心之所惡疾也。美惡，猶喜怒也；善不善，猶是非也。喜怒同根，是非同門，故不可得偏舉也。此六者皆陳自然不可偏舉之明數也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "自然已足，為則敗也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 24
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "智慧自備，為則偽也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "因物而用，功自彼成，故不居也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "使功在己，則功不可久也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
